playstore_details.description:
India’s Most Secure Bitcoin Wallet


Join over 1,000,000 people with the world’s leading wallet services provider - Be a part of the Bitcoin evolution, which now has a U.S. $325+ Billion market cap!

Millions of customers trust and use Bitcoin, and thousands of merchants around the world are accepting Bitcoin as payment tokens for their products and services.

■ Bitcoin India Wallet for Buy/sell (limits applicable on buy/sell via wallet), receive, store, spend and send 30+ Cryptocurrencies: It’s an all-in-one “Mobile e-Wallet” that lets you securely complete payments via digital tokens, such as Bitcoin (BTC), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Bitcoin Gold (BTG), Bit Shares (BTS), Byte coin (BCN), Club coin (CLUB), Dash (DASH), Digi Byte (DGB), Doge coin (DOGE), EOS (EOS), Ethereum (ETH), Ethereum Classic (ETC), Factom (FCT), Lisk (LSK), Litecoin (LTC), IOTA (MIOTA), Monero (XMR), NEM (XEM), NEO (NEO), OmiseGO (OMG), Ripple (XRP), SegWit2X (B2X), Siacoin (SC), Super Bitcoin (SBTC), Tron (TRX), VeChain (VEN), and Z cash (ZEC).

■ Merchant services: Accept Bitcoin through Bitcoin India digital wallet from your customers.

■ Security: Your wallet is protected with 2FA/Two-factor authentication with Google Authenticator.

Silent features include the following:

• It’s easy to use, simple, and highly secure

• You are the only one who can control and have access to your wallet.

• It’s multilingual and available in all major languages

 
Additional features include the following:

- View of your complete transactions history

- If your e-mail gets compromised, only you can access your Bitcoin India wallet, because you would still have 2fa on your phone at Google Authenticator.

- We provide great customer support, 24/7, at https://bitcoin.zendesk.com.

- All transactions are synced across all of your devices in real time and are protected by an intense bank-level security protocol.

- Bank-level security protocol is provided to provide the highest levels of security to the tokens/funds stored in your mobile e-wallet.


About Bitcoin India

Bitcoin India Software Services Pvt. Ltd. is a private company based in India, it's the one-and-only startup from India providing these types of products and services under one umbrella, the types of tools that every person requires in the crypto space, such as a full-stack digital asset exchange and trade platform (we offer white label licensing), digital asset wallet services, a merchant payment gateway, club membership, mining services and a mining pool.

 Bitcoin India is the longest-running, one-and-only Indian exchange and wallet services provider that owns a technology to operate Global “Mining Pool” ( https://pool.bitcoin-india.org/ ).

Customer support can be reached at: care@bitcoin-india.org

For more information, please visit us at https://www.bitcoin-india.org
